name: KETAMINE
description:
Substances, legal or illegal, they all
have a story to tell. Ketamine is a
dissociative psychedelic used
medically as a veterinary and human
anaesthetic. When used in a
recreational context, ketamine is
usually injected intramuscularly,
intravenously or insufflated (snorted).
It is less often consumed orally, and
even more rarely used rectally. Its
legal status varies around the world.
